                          Meeting Schedule for 2002

   Date

   Location

   Subject

Thursday,
February 7th

   Business Meeting:
   9:30 a.m. - 10:30 a.m.

   Press Conference:
   10:30 a.m - 12:30 p.m.


Washington, DC

   The Ballroom (first floor)
   Phoenix Park Hotel
   580 N. Capitol Street, NW Washington, DC 20015

   Business Meeting and Press Conference:

   To announce the final Council-approved action plan for a rationalized
   and restructured national rail passenger system.

   As changes and additions are made to this schedule, updated information
   will be posted on this Website.

   Meetings are always open to the public unless it is specifically
   stated.

   Last updated January 22, 2002
